O.title: Realty Income Declares Dividend Increase
O.text: March 13 (Reuters) - Realty Income Corp <O.N>::124TH COMMON STOCK MONTHLY DIVIDEND INCREASE DECLARED BY REALTY INCOME.REALTY INCOME CORP: DECLARED AN INCREASE IN CO'S COMMON STOCK MONTHLY CASH DIVIDEND TO $0.2570 PER SHARE FROM $0.2565 PER SHARE.
